trans-unit.source:

\n
trans-unit.target: $x$x$Xxxx xx xxxx x xxxxx xxxxxxxxxx xxxxxxx xx xxxxx xxx xxxxxxx xx x xxx xxxxxx.$$x$$x

trans-unit.source:
\n

\ntrue if the process should be started without creating a new window to contain it; otherwise, false.

trans-unit.source:
\n

The Active Directory domain to use when starting the process.
trans-unit.target: $x$x$Xxx Xxxxxx Xxxxxxxxx xxxxxx xx xxx xxxx xxxxxxxx xxx xxxxxxx.

trans-unit.source:
The domain property is primarily of interest to users within enterprise environments that use Active Directory.

\n

trans-unit.target: $x$x$Xxxx xx xxxx xxx xxxx xxxx xx xx xxxx xxxx xxxxxxxx xxx xxxxxxx.$$x$$x

trans-unit.source:

The user name to use when starting the process.

trans-unit.source:
